#: contents/ui/config/ConfigAiChat.qml:538
msgid ""
"<ul><li>OpenAI, OpenRouter, Google, Perplexity and Anthropic require network "
"access and an API key.</li><li>Open WebUI uses its OpenAI-compatible API at "
"your configured server URL and can optionally use a bearer token; both the "
"server root and an /api URL are accepted.</li><li>Ollama connects to a local "
"server (default: http://127.0.0.1:11434).</li></ul>"
msgstr "<ul><li>OpenAI, OpenRouter, Google, Perplexity and Anthropic require network access and an API key.</li><li>Open WebUI uses its OpenAI-compatible API at your configured server URL and can optionally use a bearer token; both the server root and an /api URL are accepted.</li><li>Ollama connects to a local server (default: http://127.0.0.1:11434).</li></ul>"

